markdownRemark.html:
I’am open to new projects and problems to resolve. If you have some interesting issue, just write to me a message! I’m interesting into all kind of cooperation:

  • Start a new project
  • Create new library
  • Help with refactoring
  • Help with programming/coding problems
  • Do a workshop
  • And others…
